title: i still havent recieved my gift...
body: as said in title its past the 23 and I still haven't received the icon or riot kayle

replies.body: We're still getting these out [until the 30th,](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-23-Anniversary-gifts-are-still-being-sent-out-and-will-be-added-by-Sept-30-) so please let me know if you don't have anything by then.
Thank you, I did receive my gift shortly after your reply :)
